      'Real-time backups',
      '24/7 uptime monitoring',
      'Daily performance reports',
      'Dedicated support line',
      'Unlimited content updates',
      'Priority bug fixes',
      'Advanced speed optimization',
      'SEO monitoring',
      'Monthly strategy call',
    ],
    cta: {
      text: 'Contact for Premium',
      href: '/contact?service=maintenance&plan=premium',
    },
  },
];

/**
 * FAQ items specific to maintenance
 */
const faqItems = [
  {
    question: 'Why do I need website maintenance?',
    answer: 'Websites require regular updates to stay secure, fast, and functional. Without maintenance, your site becomes vulnerable to hackers, may slow down over time, and can experience compatibility issues. Regular maintenance protects your investment and ensures your customers always have a great experience.',
  },
  {
    question: 'What happens if my website goes down?',
    answer: 'With our maintenance plans, we monitor your site 24/7. If your site goes down, we\'re alerted immediately and begin troubleshooting right away. Most issues are resolved within hours, and we\'ll keep you informed throughout the process.',
